1. Press the COPY icon, and then go onto the blooket website - https://blooket.com/

2. Right click anywhere on the blooket homepage

3. It should come up with a list of options, find the one that says [Inspect]

4. Once you have pressed the [Inspect] option, it should come up with a command/side panel on the right have side of your tab. 
  Click on the console option at the top bar of the panel, and put in the code 'allow pasting' then press ENTER.

5. After you have done Step 4, copy the Code from the [Cheats] Folder and paste all of it into the Inspect Console.

6. Press Enter and Enjoy!
